miml.classifiers.miml.neural

Class EnMIMLNNmetric_MIMLWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • miml.classifiers.miml.MIMLClassifier
      • miml.classifiers.miml.neural.EnMIMLNNmetric_MIMLWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, IMIMLClassifier, IConfiguration, mulan.classifier.MultiLabelLearner

    public class EnMIMLNNmetric_MIMLWrapper
extends MIMLClassifier

    Class to execute the EnMIMLNNmetric algorithm for MIML data. For more information, see Wu, J. S., Huang, S. J., & Zhou, Z. H. (2014). Genome-wide protein function prediction through multi-instance multi-label learning. IEEE/ACM Transactions on Computational Biology and Bioinformatics, 11(5), 891-902..

    Version:
    20211027
    Author:
    Eva Gibaja, Amelia Zafra
